name: Femi's Army: Lead the Charge
description:
Footsteps.Bare skin.
Humidity and heat.
They walked it all without nuance.
Without missing a beat.
Creeping over the bushes.
Scattering behind trees.
Armour beaten into strengthened camouflage.
Heavy enough to weaken the knees.
Hopeful hearts beating as one.
Faith and faithless unite.
Their leader will see his calling.
Will it be tonight?
